---
import TemplateLayout from "@/templates/accounting-editorial/TemplateLayout.astro";
---

<TemplateLayout
  title="About Us | Strategic Insight Advisory"
  description="The people and philosophy behind Strategic Insight Advisory's strategic advisory practice."
  active="about"
  canonicalPath="/templates/accounting-editorial/about"
>
<main class="mt-20">
<!-- Hero Section: Strategic Wayfinders -->
<section class="relative py-section-padding px-si-margin-desktop max-w-7xl mx-auto overflow-visible">
<!-- Path Element -->
<svg class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-full -z-10 opacity-20" fill="none" viewbox="0 0 400 600">
<path class="path-line" d="M400 50 C 250 50, 250 250, 100 250 S 100 450, -50 450" stroke="#a23f00" stroke-width="1"></path>
<rect fill="#a23f00" height="10" width="10" x="95" y="245"></rect>
</svg>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-gutter items-center">
<div class="md:col-span-7">
<span class="text-secondary font-si-label-lg text-si-label-lg tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 block">Our Identity</span>
<h1 class="font-si-display-lg text-si-display-lg text-primary mb-8 leading-tight">Strategic <br/>Wayfinders.</h1>
<p class="font-si-body-lg text-si-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl">
                        At Strategic Insight Advisory, we don't just account for the past; we find the path to your future. It's about seeing the bigger picture while minding the smallest details.
                    </p>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-5 relative mt-12 md:mt-0">
<div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-surface-container overflow-hidden editorial-shadow">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700" data-alt="A professional, high-end editorial portrait of a diverse team of strategists in a modern, sunlit architectural office. The scene features deep plum accents and warm orange highlights in the decor, reflecting a corporate yet visionary atmosphere. Soft morning light streams through large windows, creating a bright and clean light-mode aesthetic that emphasizes clarity and intellectual depth." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDygrVM3Tub4WGRMLZw01VWXpR7yIkHtjnhQL7Ft76-maHzznnpI-vZC23s5mQghBSaU4ibdNPCO1HejEVPtvXZz2tnYQfhUKT4iNv_90TfcYbQqBeCa-7OSOBfp9p4bHcEZuDBKUAwrivPLBdatVCgcDkaYsRriicYygugoIcuCxGwgqs7jckDvgeFwUc9dqeua0oCRqRfYXziswpjG1zLjS67SDLNcdaAz4uRkV7xX4lkeAhXMMua1oyWDf3O4x1fKcFzY2kYeYxj"/>
</div>
<!-- Path Marker -->
<div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 w-12 h-12 bg-secondary flex items-center justify-center">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-primary" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">trending_up</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Who We Are / Narrative -->
<section class="bg-primary text-on-primary py-section-padding px-si-margin-desktop overflow-hidden">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
<div>
<h2 class="font-si-headline-lg text-si-headline-lg mb-8">Who we are <br/>and what we do.</h2>
<div class="h-1 w-24 bg-secondary mb-12"></div>
</div>
<div class="space-y-8 font-si-body-lg text-si-body-lg opacity-90 leading-relaxed">
<p>
                        We’re passionate about our business. But it’s all about helping clients like you achieve the goals of your business. Which takes far more than spreadsheets and compliance.
                    </p>
<p>
                        It takes a commitment to deeply understand your unique challenges, solve problems with sound methods, proactively identify trends and seize opportunities before they pass.
                    </p>
<div class="pt-4">
<a class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 group text-secondary-fixed-dim font-bold" href="/templates/accounting-editorial/services">
                            Our Method 
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">arrow_forward</span>
</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Stats Grid: Global Presence -->
<section class="py-section-padding px-si-margin-desktop max-w-7xl mx-auto relative">
<!-- Asymmetric Grid for Stats -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-gutter text-center md:text-left">
<div class="p-8 border-l border-outline-variant hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-all">
<h3 class="font-si-display-lg text-si-display-lg text-primary mb-2">1,500+</h3>
<p class="font-si-label-lg text-si-label-lg text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-widest">Professionals</p>
</div>
<div class="p-8 border-l border-outline-variant mt-8 md:mt-12 hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-all">
<h3 class="font-si-display-lg text-si-display-lg text-secondary mb-2">94+</h3>
<p class="font-si-label-lg text-si-label-lg text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-widest">Years in Business</p>
</div>
<div class="p-8 border-l border-outline-variant hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-all">
<h3 class="font-si-display-lg text-si-display-lg text-primary mb-2">25</h3>
<p class="font-si-label-lg text-si-label-lg text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-widest">Offices Worldwide</p>
</div>
<div class="p-8 border-l border-outline-variant mt-8 md:mt-12 hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-all">
<h3 class="font-si-display-lg text-si-display-lg text-secondary mb-2">84</h3>
<p class="font-si-label-lg text-si-label-lg text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-widest">Net Promoter Score</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Path Connector Line -->
<svg class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-24 -z-10" fill="none" viewbox="0 0 1200 100">
<path d="M0 50 Q 300 50, 600 50 T 1200 50" stroke="#d2c2cd" stroke-width="1"></path>
<circle cx="600" cy="50" fill="#a23f00" r="4"></circle>
</svg>
</section>
<!-- Excellence / Awards Bento Grid -->
<section class="py-section-padding px-si-margin-desktop bg-surface-container-low">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-16">
<div>
<span class="text-secondary font-si-label-lg text-si-label-lg tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 block">Recognition</span>
<h2 class="font-si-headline-lg text-si-headline-lg text-primary">Strategic Insight Advisory <br/>Excellence</h2>
</div>
<div class="hidden md:block text-right">
<p class="font-si-body-md text-on-surface-variant max-w-xs italic border-r-2 border-secondary pr-6">
                            Consistently ranked among the top elite firms in the nation for performance and expertise.
                        </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-gutter">
<!-- Award Card 1 -->
<div class="bg-surface p-12 border border-outline-variant hover:shadow-lg transition-all group">
<div class="text-secondary font-si-display-lg text-si-display-lg mb-4">Best</div>
<h4 class="font-si-headline-sm text-si-headline-sm text-primary mb-2">Inside Public Accounting</h4>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant font-si-label-lg">Best of the Best Accounting Firm</p>
<div class="mt-8 h-1 w-0 bg-secondary group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-500"></div>
</div>
<!-- Award Card 2 -->
<div class="bg-surface p-12 border border-outline-variant hover:shadow-lg transition-all group md:translate-y-8">
<div class="text-primary font-si-display-lg text-si-display-lg mb-4">Top 100</div>
<h4 class="font-si-headline-sm text-si-headline-sm text-primary mb-2">Inside Public Accounting</h4>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant font-si-label-lg">Top 50 Firm Nationwide</p>
<div class="mt-8 h-1 w-0 bg-primary group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-500"></div>
</div>
<!-- Award Card 3 -->
<div class="bg-surface p-12 border border-outline-variant hover:shadow-lg transition-all group">
<div class="text-secondary font-si-display-lg text-si-display-lg mb-4">No. 1</div>
<h4 class="font-si-headline-sm text-si-headline-sm text-primary mb-2">Callahan &amp; Associates</h4>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant font-si-label-lg">Credit Union Auditing Firm</p>
<div class="mt-8 h-1 w-0 bg-secondary group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-500"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Values: Our Guiding Principles -->
<section class="py-section-padding px-si-margin-desktop max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-24 items-center">
<div class="relative">
<div class="aspect-square bg-surface-container relative overflow-hidden">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="A sophisticated abstract architectural photograph focusing on sharp angles, glass reflections, and structural lines. The image is bathed in a deep plum and crisp off-white color palette, capturing the essence of corporate expertise and strategic clarity. Subtle orange light reflects off a metallic surface, providing a focal point of energy and forward-thinking direction." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuClCPvfi7VprmHau75rhEkzTDvD33wimmoPp2EQt173JGv9dv7FEWFg7rhkRRcHQpj0FgLYR0Qo_xn7qa4Vr7riHHunQ59y9oSyad4GZVdOyJWFyLOGcW3H_ZHvWpZHKCMf9wQYEtvbwHyiMFFqDaWDtuz43w5F25g17qG7ol0MKLfhBU89Zq6S14Z4OfX_huhtz1QGZReA3IcsymmpiX4KOapLF9Vir16PzU9oFNWuOQ_cdIp-vz6uP4z_g5yds1GGcUeyF5t13BCy"/>
</div>
<div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-40 h-40 bg-secondary opacity-10 rounded-full"></div>
</div>
<div class="space-y-12">
<div>
<span class="text-secondary font-si-label-lg text-si-label-lg tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 block">Values</span>
<h2 class="font-si-headline-lg text-si-headline-lg text-primary mb-6">Built on Insight, Driven by Strategy.</h2>
</div>
<div class="space-y-8">
<div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-3xl">lightbulb</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-si-headline-sm text-si-headline-sm mb-2">Intellectual Depth</h4>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">We dive deeper to uncover nuances that others miss, providing clarity in complexity.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-3xl">hub</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-si-headline-sm text-si-headline-sm mb-2">Connected Thinking</h4>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">Our global network ensures that every local insight is backed by worldwide perspective.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-3xl">verified</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-si-headline-sm text-si-headline-sm mb-2">Unyielding Integrity</h4>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">Strategic guidance is only as valuable as the trust upon which it is built.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Careers Call-to-Action -->
<section class="bg-primary-container py-24 px-si-margin-desktop text-center relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto relative z-10">
<h2 class="font-si-headline-lg text-si-headline-lg text-on-primary mb-8">Join the Wayfinders.</h2>
<p class="font-si-body-lg text-si-body-lg text-on-primary opacity-80 mb-12">
                    We're looking for visionary thinkers who value intellectual rigour and professional growth.
                </p>
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 justify-center">
<a class="bg-secondary text-on-primary px-10 py-4 font-si-label-lg text-si-label-lg uppercase tracking-widest hover:scale-105 transition-all" href="/templates/accounting-editorial/contact">View Openings</a>
<a class="border border-on-primary text-on-primary px-10 py-4 font-si-label-lg text-si-label-lg uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-on-primary hover:text-primary transition-all" href="/templates/accounting-editorial/contact">Our Culture</a>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Decorative Element -->
<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
<svg class="w-full h-full" preserveaspectratio="none" viewbox="0 0 100 100">
<path d="M0 100 L100 0" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.1"></path>
<path d="M0 80 L80 0" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.1"></path>
<path d="M20 100 L100 20" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.1"></path>
</svg>
</div>
</section>
</main>

</TemplateLayout>
